{"tid":2372786,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金融時報：美國對沖基金Elliott擬關閉本港辦事處","createTime":"2021-01-20T03:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T09:52:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffdaf5950bc6b7480a87b3281b150eb2fc0fb75f","tid":2372786,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"對沖基金Elliott擬關閉本港辦事處 <br />\n<br />\n英國金融時報報道，美國對沖基金Elliott Management Corp計劃關閉香港辦事處，將剩餘員工調至倫敦和東京的辦公室，東京成為基金在亞洲的唯一基地。基金於今年1月1日停止交易和投資活動。 <br />\n<br />\nElliott Management由富豪辛格(Paul Singer)於1977年創立，截至去年底管理資產逾450億美元。基金較為人熟悉的舉動，是2014年入股東亞銀行(<a href=\"http://00023.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00023.HK&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeswCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=62707b83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00023.HK</a>)後，多次要求李國寶家族出售資產，其後東亞去年宣布全面檢討資產業務，獲Elliott表態支持 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2375534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F2375534&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeswCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=63111780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2375534</a>"},{"pid":"c376f420154c37b1a5e7e1d144d1c86a28fff2eb","tid":2372786,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:15:40.000Z","msg":"但邱局長睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a303ee37adf5bcdf2332992a893bd07116fa9c","tid":2372786,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"Donki好多人，唔怕!"},{"pid":"b8949e1c09068307290abe91d9b458c1e23edd15","tid":2372786,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"腐乳華：只有中資公司才是外資"},{"pid":"c4e4db4842b63775d99b4a04be6801dfeb305462","tid":2372786,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"樓價 gogogo <br />\n<br />\n新盤賣哂 <img src=\"/ass